{"tid":852882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太扯！6歲男童左陰囊積水 醫生竟「左右不分」切錯邊","createTime":"2018-10-08T07:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T12:45:57.000Z","uid":205996,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"474a19fc8dd8b9b24b22211ff0b15d8edf633daa","tid":852882,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-08/656/20181008002499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-08%2F656%2F20181008002499.jpg&h=7708f816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有夠誇張！大陸河南鄭州一名6歲男童的睪丸大小不一，檢查後發現是左側陰囊積水，近日家人帶他到醫院接受手術，沒想到醫生竟然左右不分，在男童的右側陰囊開刀，原本應該治療的左側陰囊反而原封不動。醫生之後坦承疏失，但卻強調家屬也有責任，令家屬完全不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒報導，男童父親憤怒表示，因為兒子的睪丸大小不一，醫生建議立刻動手術，否則會影響生育，因此聽從建議照做，沒想到開完刀發現，兒子積水的左側陰囊沒被動刀，反而是右側陰囊莫名挨刀，原來，兒子的病歷從頭到尾都被寫上「右側」，連年齡都寫錯，讓他傻眼地說「左和右這麽簡單的事，還分不清嗎？醫師也犯這麽低級的錯誤？」<br />\n<br />\n事後負責開刀的李姓醫師坦承疏失，有可能是因為太過忙碌，才沒時間詳細查看男童的病歷，但也有可能是與家屬溝通時出了問題，「不知道是當時家屬跟我說錯了，還是我記錯了」，這樣的說法讓男童的父親完全無法接受，但他目前只希望轉院的兒子平安無事、不會影響生育。"},{"pid":"abd5f1e286f297f2b452ebe6aa15240a13ea3afe","tid":852882,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"想斷人後代"},{"pid":"e8de3187d48235608e4b137cbf4acdad48178fe5","tid":852882,"uid":206176,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"扯你老味"},{"pid":"3365a734e7abcac093100c2ca30989a50e0e7f36","tid":852882,"uid":14103,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"支那多幾個依種醫生就好了"},{"pid":"d5ac059bf4581cc6d460994cc81d1a39676b226c","tid":852882,"uid":131686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"肥絲呢"},{"pid":"576a4f9c01991e007a6f5ba436bcf5a14fe2bbff","tid":852882,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c4fd390bb0f25bcff0a896af35b69d4788ee266","tid":852882,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:00:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d9463a55778b86a73493468abab1411de9a368b","tid":852882,"uid":3268,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"醫生:你左邊姐係邊係我左定右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求撚其其又收幾皮<br />\n是但切一邊la<br />\n面對我左邊姐係你左la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af595755f418d74c1a4982d468e949acc36e838","tid":852882,"uid":182499,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"肥絲做醫生？切埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaad00dd91db765d42428a1f445f3ff98862bcbb","tid":852882,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"淨番一粒積水嘅，切唔切好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e266c243d96a56b66620c44dcd93129db061573c","tid":852882,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"單丸也是正常"},{"pid":"829ccc0f7819898f1a5efac4ad2e200c0fa14627","tid":852882,"uid":21310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9067a035c74310d65735652a35865b47dcdfb5b","tid":852882,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:31:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5ed3816d6bbb5e7b2e3800c1cd0760100869b15","tid":852882,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9af595755f418d74c1a4982d468e949acc36e838","tid":852882,"uid":182499,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"肥絲做醫生？切埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"係肥絲就會切左切埋右 兩邊一齊切啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d97cb080